Class RoomServer

  • java.lang.Object
    • server.Server
      • server.RoomServer
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    game.MoveNotifier, ServerInterpreter

    public class RoomServer
extends Server
implements game.MoveNotifier
    Server room handler. Controls the game state and player movements. checks if they do not cheat and sends over messages.

      • RoomServer

        public RoomServer(game.MoveNotifier master,
                  game.Board.Size size,
                  boolean BlackAI,
                  boolean WhiteAI,
                  java.lang.String RoomName)
        Default Constructor
        Parameters:
        master - master of this component. Should be used as a way to close Room Server with ability to inform Users. Also RoomServer will notify Master when the game ends and it can be disposed naturally.
        size - Size of board
        BlackAI - Whether black player is AI
        WhiteAI - Whether white player is AI
        RoomName - Name of room
        Throws:
        java.lang.NullPointerException - If info is a null pointer
